description:
Sicily is one of Italy's best destinations. Enjoy this travel guide across Sicily's incredible places. From the medieval seaside town of Cefalù, to the volcanic Aeolian Islands, Sicily has so much to offer. Where is your favorite place in Sicily?

My relaxation channel - https://www.youtube.com/scenicrelaxationfilms

My Travel Videos: 

Top 10 Places Aeolian Islands - https://youtu.be/ozpGTw6DrXs

Top 100 Places in Italy - https://youtu.be/02jQiIkEGh8

Top 10 Places in Tuscany - https://youtu.be/7aNxp7ybmX8
